{"title":"Gnomish helm","url":"https://nethackwiki.com/wiki/Gnomish_helm","type":"markdown","data":"| \\[   gnomish helm   |                                      |\n| ------------------- | ------------------------------------ |\n| Appearance          | little red hat                       |\n|                     |                                      |\n| Slot                | [helm](/wiki/Helm \"Helm\")            |\n| AC                  | [0](/wiki/Armor_class \"Armor class\") |\n| Special             | *(none)*                             |\n|                     |                                      |\n| Base price          | 8 [zm](/wiki/Zorkmid \"Zorkmid\")      |\n| Weight              | [3](/wiki/Weight \"Weight\")           |\n| Material            | [cloth](/wiki/Cloth \"Cloth\")         |\n\nA **gnomish helm** is a type of [helm](/wiki/Helm \"Helm\") that appears in [SporkHack](/wiki/SporkHack \"SporkHack\") and [SlashTHEM](/wiki/SlashTHEM \"SlashTHEM\"). It is made of [cloth](/wiki/Cloth \"Cloth\") and appears as a **little red hat** when unidentified.\n\n## Generation\n\nEvery non-[undead](/wiki/Undead \"Undead\") [gnome](/wiki/Gnome_\\(monster_class\\) \"Gnome (monster class)\") has a chance of [being generated](/wiki/Monster_starting_inventory \"Monster starting inventory\") with a gnomish helm, making them very common in the [Gnomish Mines](/wiki/Gnomish_Mines \"Gnomish Mines\").\n\n## Description\n\nWhen worn, a gnomish helm provides a base [AC](/wiki/AC \"AC\") of 0, but gives a +2 [racial equipment](/wiki/Racial_equipment \"Racial equipment\") AC bonus to [gnomish](/wiki/Gnome_\\(starting_race\\) \"Gnome (starting race)\") characters that wear them.\n\n## Strategy\n\nGnomish helms are naturally most useful to gnomish characters, though a gnome character in SlashTHEM may have a hard time finding them in the Mines due to the lack of friendly gnomes within.\n\n- *This page is a **[stub](/wiki/Category:Stubs \"Category:Stubs\")**. Should you wish to do so, you can contribute by [**expanding this page**.](https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Gnomish_helm\\&action=edit)*\n\n[![This article describes a 3.4.3-based variant of NetHack. Click here for more information.](/images/5/5d/Nh343var-icon.png)](/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version \"This article describes a 3.4.3-based variant of NetHack. Click here for more information.\")\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Gnomish helm - NetHack Wiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Gnomish_helm\",\"wgTitle\":\"Gnomish helm\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":160903,\"wgRevisionId\":160903,\"wgArticleId\":38014,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"Stubs\",\"Variant-343 articles\",\"SporkHack helms\",\"SlashTHEM helms\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\",\"Sep\",\"Oct\",\"Nov\",\"Dec\"],\"wgRelevantPageName\":\"Gnomish_helm\",\"wgRelevantArticleId\":38014,\"wgRequestId\":\"28c7fd0911a0f9d00fcd6b2b\",\"wgCSPNonce\":false,\"wgIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRelevantPageIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRestrictionEdit\":[],\"wgRestrictionMove\":[],\"wgWikiEditorEnabledModules\":[],\"wgCategoryTreePageCategory