_helm\"/>\n<!--[if lt IE 9]><script src=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=html5shiv&amp;only=scripts&amp;skin=vector&amp;sync=1\"></script><![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body class=\"mediawiki ltr sitedir-ltr mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Gnomish_helm rootpage-Gnomish_helm skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Gnomish helm</h1>\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From NetHackWiki</div>\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\"></div>\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#mw-head\">Jump to navigation</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#p-search\">Jump to search</a>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"margin: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" style=\"font-size:larger;\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-red\">[</span> &#8194; gnomish helm &#8194;\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Appearance\n</th>\n<td>little red hat\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Slot\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Helm\" title=\"Helm\">helm</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>AC\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Armor_class\" title=\"Armor class\">0</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Special\n</th>\n<td><i>(none)</i>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Base price\n</th>\n<td>8 <a href=\"/wiki/Zorkmid\" title=\"Zorkmid\">zm</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Weight\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Weight\" title=\"Weight\">3</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Material\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Cloth\" title=\"Cloth\">cloth</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p>A <b>gnomish helm</b> is a type of <a href=\"/wiki/Helm\" title=\"Helm\">helm</a> that appears in <a href=\"/wiki/SporkHack\" title=\"SporkHack\">SporkHack</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/SlashTHEM\" title=\"SlashTHEM\">SlashTHEM</a>. It is made of <a href=\"/wiki/Cloth\" title=\"Cloth\">cloth</a> and appears as a <b>little red hat</b> when unidentified.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Generation\">Generation</span></h2>\n<p>Every non-<a href=\"/wiki/Undead\" title=\"Undead\">undead</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Gnome_(monster_class)\" title=\"Gnome (monster class)\">gnome</a> has a chance of <a href=\"/wiki/Monster_starting_inventory\" title=\"Monster starting inventory\">being generated</a> with a gnomish helm, making them very common in the <a href=\"/wiki/Gnomish_Mines\" title=\"Gnomish Mines\">Gnomish Mines</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Description\">Description</span></h2>\n<p>When worn, a gnomish helm provides a base <a href=\"/wiki/AC\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"AC\">AC</a> of 0, but gives a +2 <a href=\"/wiki/Racial_equipment\" title=\"Racial equipment\">racial equipment</a> AC bonus to <a href=\"/wiki/Gnome_(starting_race)\" title=\"Gnome (starting race)\">gnomish</a> characters that wear them.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Strategy\">Strategy</span></h2>\n<p>Gnomish helms are naturally most useful to gnomish characters, though a gnome character in SlashTHEM may have a hard time finding them in the Mines due to the lack of friendly gnomes within.\n</p>\n<div class=\"stub\">\n<dl><dd><i>This page is a <b><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Stubs\" title=\"Category:Stubs\">stub</a></b>. Should you wish to do so, you can contribute by <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Gnomish_helm&amp;action=edit\"><b>expanding this page</b>.</a></i></dd></dl>\n</div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -1