\" 35.06%    4.671      1 Template:Variant-343\",\" 30.35%    4.043      1 Template:Autotile\",\" 25.40%    3.384      1 Template:Version_icon\",\" 20.28%    2.702      1 Template:LinklessExists\",\" 15.40%    2.052      1 Template:Top_icon\",\" 10.80%    1.439      1 Template:Stub\",\"  8.61%    1.147      1 Template:Red\"]},\"cachereport\":{\"timestamp\":\"20240926183828\",\"ttl\":604800,\"transientcontent\":false}}});mw.config.set({\"wgBackendResponseTime\":61});});</script>\n\t</body>\n</html>\n","rawPage":"{{armor\n  |color=red\n  |name=gnomish helm\n  |appearance=little red hat\n  |cost=8\n  |slot=helm\n  |ac=0\n  |weight=3\n  |material=cloth\n}}\n\nA '''gnomish helm''' is a type of [[helm]] that appears in [[SporkHack]] and [[SlashTHEM]]. It is made of [[cloth]] and appears as a '''little red hat''' when unidentified.\n\n==Generation==\nEvery non-[[undead]] [[Gnome (monster class)|gnome]] has a chance of [[Monster starting inventory|being generated]] with a gnomish helm, making them very common in the [[Gnomish Mines]].\n\n==Description==\nWhen worn, a gnomish helm provides a base [[AC]] of 0, but gives a +2 [[racial equipment]] AC bonus to [[Gnome (starting race)|gnomish]] characters that wear them.\n\n==Strategy==\nGnomish helms are naturally most useful to gnomish characters, though a gnome character in SlashTHEM may have a hard time finding them in the Mines due to the lack of friendly gnomes within.\n{{stub}}\n{{variant-343}}\n[[Category:SporkHack helms]]\n[[Category:SlashTHEM helms]]"}